text: "Kids" is a 2016 song by American pop rock band OneRepublic and is the second single from their fourth studio album Oh My My. It went to number 1 in New Zealand, number 21 in the Czech Republic, number 26 in Spain and number 30 in Hungary. It also peaked at number 58 in the United Kingdom, number 63 in Australia, number 66 in Ireland and number 96 in the United States and did not chart in Canada.
